ComicInfo.Summary:
Sacrifice is the common theme of Angel’s existence up to this point—and her stay in Rome ends with her losing someone very close to her in a shocking and bloody fashion! The gruesome finale to the “A Dead Girl in Europe” story arc shatters the future for everyone’s favorite new Zombie Tramp!
Features 3 regular and risqué variants, including two featured artist variants!!!
